{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"id7ab2994b-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9573"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"9573"},"text":"§ 9573.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Duties","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id7ab2994c-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9573/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" In general","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"The Council shall provide advice to the Under Secretary by—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id7ab2994d-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9573/a/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" serving as a source of knowledge and information on developments in areas of the economic and social life of the United States that affect socially or economically disadvantaged business concerns;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id7ab2994e-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9573/a/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" providing the Under Secretary with information regarding plans, programs, and activities in the public and private sectors that relate to socially or economically disadvantaged business concerns; and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id7ab2994f-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9573/a/3"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3"},"text":"(3)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":" advising the Under Secretary regarding—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id7ab29950-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9573/a/3/A"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"A"},"text":"(A)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" any measures to better achieve the objectives of this chapter; and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id7ab29951-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9573/a/3/B"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"B"},"text":"(B)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" problems and matters the Under Secretary refers to the Council.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id7ab29952-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9573/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Capacity","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Members of the Council shall not be compensated for service on the Council but may be allowed travel expenses, including per diem in lieu of subsistence, in accordance with subchapter I of chapter 57 of title 5.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id7ab29953-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9573/c"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"c"},"text":"(c)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Termination","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Notwithstanding section 14 of the Federal Advisory Committee Act (5 U.S.C. App.),","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"idref":"fn002667"},"text":"1","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"type":"footnote","id":"fn002667"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{},"text":"1","children":[],"tail":" See References in Text note below."}],"tail":" the Council shall terminate on the date that is 5 years after "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2021-11-15"},"text":"November 15, 2021","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"id7ab29954-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/117/58/dK/tV/s100503"},"text":"Pub. L. 117–58, div. K, title V, § 100503","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2021-11-15"},"text":"Nov. 15, 2021","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/135/1463"},"text":"135 Stat. 1463","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"id7ab29955-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"id7ab29956-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"id7ab29957-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"This chapter, referred to in subsec. (a)(3)(A), was in the original “this division”, meaning div. K of ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/117/58"},"text":"Pub. L. 117–58","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2021-11-15"},"text":"Nov. 15, 2021","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/135/1445"},"text":"135 Stat. 1445","children":[],"tail":", which is classified prinicpally to this chapter. For complete classification of division K to the Code, see Short Title note set out under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t15/s9501"},"text":"section 9501 of this title","children":[],"tail":" and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section 14 of the Federal Advisory Committee Act, referred to in subsec. (c), is ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/92/463/s14"},"text":"section 14 of Pub. L. 92–463","children":[],"tail":", which was set out in the Appendix to Title 5, Government Organization and Employees, and was repealed and restated as "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t5/s1013"},"text":"section 1013 of Title 5","children":[],"tail":" by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/117/286"},"text":"Pub. L. 117–286","children":[],"tail":", §§ 3(a), 7, "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2022-12-27"},"text":"Dec. 27, 2022","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/136/4204"},"text":"136 Stat. 4204","children":[],"tail":", 4361."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
